These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
There 4 different types of food: grapes, orange, avocado, cucumber
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, french, pakistani, polish
1. the french is on the left of the brazilian##1
2. the person eating grapes is the polish##1
3. the pakistani is on the right of the brazilian##1
4. the person eating orange is on the left of the polish##1
5. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | cucumber | avocado | orange | grapes   |
| Nationality   | french  | brazilian     | pakistani   | polish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, dancing, magic-tricks, hiking
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, cricket, golf, weightlifting
1. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person who's sport is cricket##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
4. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
5. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | hiking | dancing | fishing    |
| Sport   | golf    | cricket      | badminton | weightlifting |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, camping, filmmaking, reading
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, satire, spy, documentary
1. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
2. the person who's hobby is chess is the person watching adventure movies##1
3. the person watching satire movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby         | chess | reading | filmmaking   | camping |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure   | spy | documentary | satire         |

