.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, spy, martial-arts, family
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, skateboarding, biathlon, parkour
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person watching family movies##1
2. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
3. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
4. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | family | spy | romance  | martial-arts      |
| Sport         | skateboarding | parkour   | biathlon | ice-hockey |

