.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, blueberry, apricot, asparagus
4 different pets are kept: bird, frog, ferret, turtle
1. the person eating blueberry is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1
2. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
3. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
4. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Food   | asparagus | apricot | blueberry | grapefruit |
| Pet    | bird       | turtle | ferret | frog     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: french, colombian, british, egyptian
4 different pets are kept: lizard, bird, rabbit, pony
1. the colombian is on the far right##1
2. the egyptian is on the left of the british##1
3. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
4. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the british##1
5. the owner of the pony is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Nationality   | egyptian | british | french | colombian |
| Pet           | lizard      | rabbit | pony | bird    |

