2. the fan of gospel is on the far right##1
3. the fan of blues is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the goldfish is on the far right##1
5. the fan of disco is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | blues | disco | house | gospel  |
| Pet           | rabbit | frog | turtle       | goldfish |

