.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dressmaker, nurse, photographer, manager
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, boat, motorbike, airplane
1. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the nurse##1
2. the person driving the airplane is the manager##1
3. the nurse is on the right of the dressmaker##1
4. the photographer is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
5. the person driving the van is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Job         | photographer | dressmaker      | nurse | manager |
| Transport   | van          | boat | motorbike     | airplane    |

