.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, lemonade, 7up
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, airplane, van, subway
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the van##1
4. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| Beverage    | almond-milk | lemonade  | coffee | 7up |
| Transport   | subway | van | airplane          | quad-bike    |

