.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, juice, cola
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, classical, funk, dubstep
1. the fan of funk is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
2. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the fan of funk##1
3. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
4. the person drinking juice is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is the fan of funk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| Beverage      | juice | almond-milk  | 7up | cola |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop  | funk | dubstep           | classical   |

