.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, turkish, dutch, italian
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, helicopter, bike, ship
1. the person driving the train is on the left of the turkish##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the italian##1
3. the spanish is on the left of the dutch##1
4. the italian is the person driving the ship##1
5. the person driving the train is on the left of the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Nationality   | spanish | dutch | turkish | italian   |
| Transport     | bike  | train    | helicopter       | ship |

 